metadata.name: Reaper#3
metadata.description: Death is an absolute truth that can not be denied. Whenever we think of death we always have scary and fearful feelings. In art culture, death is usually portrayed as a black and white Grim- Reaper which gives a feeling of death as a cold and void experience. My Grim- Reaper represents my idea of death which might be scary but a colorful and soothing experience that might relieve you of the feeling of cold and scary death.
